    "Additionally, the study explored the influence of Bag of Words (BoW), bi-grams, and tri-grams on training.",
    "It evaluated the effectiveness of kNN, NB, cNB, and EvoSVM algorithms in screening automation under these variations.",
    "Furthermore, the study delved into the effects of optimisation techniques and cross-validation on model performance.",
    "The results suggested that optimising and cross-validating BoW with full citations (title + abstract + metadata) or with title + abstract, using either cNB or EvoSVM, yielded the most favourable outcomes in terms of automation performance.",
